---

<Layout
  description="More and more people are using Google Maps over Google Search to find products and especially services as it improves results with a more localised algorithm. If your business wants to survive in the fast moving world of digital marketing you must be putting focus into your local SEO rank and score. We have been optimising our SEO strategies for local ranking over search based ranking for over 10 years. Digital marketing expertise you can truly trust. Expert digital marketing management on the Gold Coast."
