>

    <SlotHero>
      <Fragment slot="smltitle">
        Local SEO Optimisation
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Generate more local leads.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        More and more people are using Google Maps over Google Search to find products and especially services as it improves results with a more localised algorithm. If your business wants to survive in the fast moving world of digital marketing you must be putting focus into your local SEO rank and score. I have been optimising our SEO strategies for local ranking over search based ranking for over 10 years. Gold Coast digital marketing management and expertise you can trust.
      </Fragment>
      
    </SlotHero>

    <FirstProcess />
    
          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Google Maps rank optimisation
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Localisized customer targeting.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              In today's digital age, your online presence is often the first impression potential customers have of your business. I'm dedicated to enhancing your online visibility and creating a compelling digital storefront that attracts local leads. With proven techniques, such as local keyword optimization, customer reviews, and on-page SEO, I'll help you generate a steady stream of local leads eager to engage with your business. When it comes to local marketing, I don't believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. Each business and location is unique, and that's why I tailor local marketing strategies to your specific needs. From optimizing your Google My Business profile to creating location-based content, I focus on strategies that bring tangible results, such as increased foot traffic, phone calls, and website visits.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-wth.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Boost Your Online Presence and Generate More Local Leads
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              The future of marketing.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Local citations are references to your business information across the web. Consistency in these citations plays a significant role in local SEO. With meticulous local citation management, I ensure that your business information, such as your name, address, and phone number (NAP), is consistent across online directories and platforms. This not only boosts your local SEO but also establishes trust with search engines and potential customers. Link building is a crucial component of SEO, and this applies to local SEO as well. I'm well-versed in crafting effective local link building strategies that help your website gain authority in your target area. By acquiring high-quality backlinks from reputable local sources, we enhance your local search rankings, making your business more visible to local searchers.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/hero-estem.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Localized Content That Speaks to Your Target Market
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Convenient customer booking.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Creating content that resonates with your local audience is a vital part of local SEO. I'll work with you to develop localized content that reflects the interests, culture, and needs of your community. This not only boosts your local SEO but also helps you connect with potential customers on a personal level, fostering a strong sense of community and loyalty. Google Maps has become an integral part of our daily lives. More than a navigation tool, it's a powerful platform for local businesses to gain visibility. Through meticulous Google Maps optimization, I'll make sure your business appears prominently on the map, making it easy for potential customers to find and visit your location. Get ready to lead the way in your local market.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-mac-render-med.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>
  
